---
description: Frontend architecture rules
globs: ["apps/web/**"]
---
- Flow: Component → Hook → Service → Gateway → Backend.
- TSX files: pure composition; a single local `XxxProps` interface is the only allowed declaration.
- Hooks own state/handlers, stay thin; complex logic goes to `features/*/lib` helpers.
- Services orchestrate; gateways do HTTP only via the shared HTTP client wrapper.
- All strings via `@/i18n` `t()`. Mobile-first (320px+), dark/light, reduced motion, a11y labels.
- Never store the uploaded image in localStorage/sessionStorage/IndexedDB. Revoke object URLs.
